The evidence with the title 'Donald Trump vs. Warren Buffett: how Buffett's taxes prove trump ... ' says Oct 10, 2016  ... Clinton also invoked Buffett during the debate , mentioning her “ Buffett rule ” proposal that would tack on a tax surcharge for people whose annual income is above $ 5 million. The proposal is named for the investor who has famously said that he should not pay a lower tax rate than his secretary . 
